('fe6a183f-64d1-53ad-8954-d526af34d899', '66d8c8b8-ae81-4c42-9c6f-a77f274b5f15', 'The debate over the legality of ___ has sparked intense protests across the country.', '關於墮胎合法性的辯論在全國引發了激烈的抗議。', 'abortion', 'adoption', 'addiction', 'election', 'abort (中止/流產) + -ion (名詞字尾) → 墮胎', '記住 abort 是「中止」的意思，加上 -ion 變成名詞，指「中止妊娠」的行為。', '2026-07-06 16:06:40', '2026-07-06 16:06:40'),
